casebody.data:
No. 10-1173. Sergeants Benevolent Association Health and Welfare Fund, on Behalf of Themselves and All Others Similarly Situated, et al., Petitioners v. Eli Lilly and Company. 564 U.S. 1046, 131 S. Ct. 3062,

180 L. Ed. 2d 903,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4918. June 27, 2011.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 620 F.3d 121.
